{"tid":189591,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"松本潤偷吃AV女優4年 井上真央出面回應了","createTime":"2017-04-06T14:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T07:01:05.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bbcd8d29741f1db704a7b1763712b3af5624ca46","tid":189591,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:06:42.000Z","msg":"松本潤偷吃AV女優4年 井上真央出面回應了<br />\n<br />\n井上真央因2005年和松本潤合作日版《流星花園》而交往，兩人長達12年的感情，卻在去年底時發生變化。松本潤因爆出偷吃AV女優葵司4年，井上真央被爆瀕臨崩潰、甚至有引退意思，可近日她外出溜狗被堵，罕見不避諱大方談此事，不僅否認要引退，甚至有些力挺松本潤，令許多網友都相當意外。<br />\n<br />\n井上真央日前被《女性自身》堵到，她一改過去低調避談風格，所有問題來者不拒，由於先前有傳兩人有意結婚，她就尷尬表示「不能在這裡說，要透過事務所回答。」但被問到婚期是否就在近期？她則否認。<br />\n<br />\n只是松本潤被爆出偷吃AV女優葵司，井上真央屢次被爆崩潰、還有引退傳聞，但她就無奈表示「這說法讓我很吃驚，但沒辦法，這工作就是會引來誤會。」她也強調自己就快要復出了，只是還沒對外公開；至於松本潤的八卦，井上真央也認為不是完全屬實，心情絲毫不受影響，但外界認為兩人真要開花結果，恐怕還有段路得走。"},{"pid":"e23c0ef59184647b939ee0ab6c21c307e4326ed7","tid":189591,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"葵司又真係好好食既"},{"pid":"c15b78a0e9802c81ac63b5658a646a34e19b2de6","tid":189591,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"個屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869c050cfbd06380df14676eefd626ff081a2e86","tid":189591,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:49:10.000Z","msg":"啜腳指都已經屈哂機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02d195e6762fd77a792a7faf98cce2cf4fc72c8","tid":189591,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fec8c5aba006adca02094d6247275df8d55cde5","tid":189591,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:42:31.000Z","msg":"葵司係咪真係有整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊期整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d2c42cc8bdf114d0139662f8ff4dbc49a2d4a5","tid":189591,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8228f438eaea25c066ea799f2a39ff7900c8057","tid":189591,"uid":1039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:22:29.000Z","msg":"葵司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9849d5be9c72a3b41803620e6e615b38c52a02ce","tid":189591,"uid":79031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:01:05.000Z","msg":"葵司副body<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}